<TD WIDTH="100%" VALIGN="TOP">&nbsp;<IMG SRC="../images/edquote.gif" WIDTH="550" HEIGHT="30" ALIGN= "BOTTOM" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3"></TD></TR>
</TABLE>
</P>

